.TH POHODA-BANK-TO-REALPAD 1 "" "pohoda-realpad" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
pohoda\-bank\-to\-realpad \- synchronize bank movements from Pohoda to Realpad
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B pohoda\-bank\-to\-realpad
[\fB\-e\fR \fIENV_FILE\fR]
[\fB\-o\fR \fIOUTPUT_FILE\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Fetches bank movements with a variable symbol from the Pohoda accounting system
and posts them to the Realpad CRM API. The result report is written as JSON to
the output file (or stdout by default).
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-e ", " \-\-environment =\fIENV_FILE\fR
Path to the environment file containing connection credentials.
.TP
.BR \-o ", " \-\-output =\fIOUTPUT_FILE\fR
Output file for the JSON result report. Defaults to stdout.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B POHODA_URL
URL of the Pohoda mServer instance.
.TP
.B POHODA_USERNAME
Pohoda mServer username.
.TP
.B POHODA_PASSWORD
Pohoda mServer password.
.TP
.B REALPAD_USERNAME
Realpad API username.
.TP
.B REALPAD_PASSWORD
Realpad API password.
.TP
.B REALPAD_PROJECT_ID
Realpad project identifier.
.TP
.B REALPAD_POHODA_WS
Override URL for the Realpad payments endpoint.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR pohoda\-bank\-to\-realpad (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>
